snippet.title: 1 Shot Pool™
snippet.description:
Play a unique pool game like never before.
In a frictionless environment, once in motion, things don't stop! 
Can you sink them all in 1 shot?!

Sink them all and your score will carry over to the next round. 
Get a high score and challenge your Game Center friends to do better!

Website: http://www.sheado.net/1shotpool
